在她的工作申请书中
She listed you as a reference

37:09.270 --> 37:10.990
他把你列为了推荐人
on her job application to work here.

37:11.000 --> 37:13.640
你很了解她么?
You know her well?

37:13.740 --> 37:18.060
如果你能把我调到隔离监狱 我对她的了解会更深
I'd know her a lot better if you can get my ass moved to Ad Seg.

37:18.070 --> 37:20.260
我在监狱部门没有影响力
(chuckles softly)I have no influence

37:20.270 --> 37:22.960
这你是知道的
with the D.O.C.--you know that.

37:23.470 --> 37:26.930
但如果你想要我的帮助 你一定可以办到
If you want my help, you do.

37:26.940 --> 37:30.430
我会跟狱长商量看看能帮上什么
I'll talk to the warden and see what I can do--

37:30.440 --> 37:32.560
只要你给我需要的答案
right after you give me some answers.

37:32.570 --> 37:35.500
斯科菲尔德喜欢通过 加密信息来和莎拉交流
Scofield likes to communicate with Sara via coded message.

37:36.000 --> 37:39.230
你能解读这些信息吗?
Do you recognize anything here?

37:39.240 --> 37:42.290
- 他在试图告诉她什么?- 不知道
Anything that he may be trying to tell her? No.

37:42.300 --> 37:44.090
我只知道他在向莎拉道歉
I mean, he's saying he's sorry.

37:44.100 --> 37:48.930
而这对冷面大夫一点好处都没有
Not that that's gonna do any good with Dr. Cold Shoulder.

37:48.940 --> 37:50.690
但是...
But...

37:50.700 --> 37:54.790
什么?
What?

37:54.800 --> 37:59.000
隔离监狱
Ad Seg.

38:01.970 --> 38:03.790
我知道了
Yeah.

38:03.800 --> 38:06.560
好吧  你来看看
All right, you see here,

38:06.570 --> 38:08.460
他说道"另一次机会"
where it says this stuff about "another chance."

38:08.470 --> 38:10.190
"安全避难所"
"Safe haven."

38:10.200 --> 38:12.290
这都是出自一本有名的书里
That's out of the big book.

38:12.300 --> 38:13.630
什么书?
What big book?

38:13.640 --> 38:15.230
"酗酒无名氏"
Alcoholics Anonymous.

38:15.240 --> 38:16.430
莎拉正在恢复中
Sara's in recovery.

38:16.440 --> 38:18.730
- 这我知道 - 这些名字他都是取自
Yeah, I'm aware of that.Those are the names

38:18.740 --> 38:22.090
那本书的章节名
of some of the chapters in the book they use in AA.

38:22.100 --> 38:25.000
你有"酗酒无名氏"这本书吗?
Do you have a copy of the Alcoholics Anonymous book?

38:27.640 --> 38:30.290
莎拉  如果你在听的话
MICHAEL: Sara, if you're listening,

38:30.300 --> 38:34.940
我知道不能奢求你"再给次机会"
I know I can't ask you for another chance.

38:37.840 --> 38:42.190
我现在只希望 你能找到"安全的避难所"
I can only hope by now you've found your safe haven.

38:45.200 --> 38:48.130
我利用了你帮助别人的承诺
I took advantage of you, your commitment to help others

38:50.140 --> 38:53.400
我却置你于一个 对每个医生来说都是噩梦的境地
and put you in a place that's every doctor's nightmare.

38:55.000 --> 38:57.090
我想过很多道歉的方式
I've considered many ways to apologize,

38:57.100 --> 39:00.770
但我必须通过一种来向你道歉
but I must arrive at one.

39:04.440 --> 39:07.190
- 天色晚了- 我知道
It's getting late.I know.

39:07.200 --> 39:08.730
她还没来
She's not here.

39:08.740 --> 39:10.860
这我也知道
I know that, too.

39:10.870 --> 39:14.290
有可能她没有收到消息
There is a chance she didn't get the message.

39:14.300 --> 39:16.330
或许她对这一切都已经厌烦了
Or maybe she's just sick of all this.

39:16.340 --> 39:18.290
忘了在基拉时  她背叛了你
The girl bailed on you back in Gila.

39:18.300 --> 39:21.590
你凭什么觉得她会回心转意?
What makes you think she's gonna come running back now?

39:21.600 --> 39:24.290
就凭着支持了我们三个月的东西
The same thing that's been keeping us going

39:24.300 --> 39:27.390
信念
for the last three months:faith.

39:27.400 --> 39:31.090
但现实会让信念消失的
Yeah, well... reality's kicking faith's ass, man.

39:31.100 --> 39:33.330
再等等吧
Look...Wait, wait.

39:33.340 --> 39:35.230
等?  老弟  我们不能再等下去了
Wait? Man, we can't wait anymore.

39:35.240 --> 39:38.160
请注意  再次呼叫迈克尔  克莱恩 (注：克莱恩暗指为折纸仙鹤)
(over P.A. system):Once again, Michael Crane,Listen, listen.

39:38.170 --> 39:39.930
请你到前台
please report to the front desk.

39:39.940 --> 39:42.230
你有电话
You have a telephone call.

39:42.240 --> 39:45.730
迈克尔  克莱恩请到前台
Michael Crane to the front desk.

39:45.740 --> 39:46.930
是的  莎拉  唐克雷蒂
Yeah. Sara Tancredi.

39:46.940 --> 39:49.590
对  有可能她现在和他们在一起
That's right. She might be with them now.

39:49.600 --> 39:51.430
对! 通知阿克隆地区的警方
Just... Yes! Just call the local police

39:51.440 --> 39:54.230
通知他们调集所有人手
in Akron and tell them to get everyone they have

39:54.240 --> 39:57.440
现在马上赶去圣托马斯医院
over to St. Thomas Hospital now.

39:59.840 --> 40:04.900
我是迈克尔  克莱恩 应该有个我的电话
Michael Crane. I think you have a call for me.

40:07.800 --> 40:10.800
谢谢
Thank you.

40:11.570 --> 40:13.190
我是克莱恩
This is Mr. Crane.

40:13.200 --> 40:16.490
这比"Origami"(日语  折纸鹤)要好听
It sounded better than "Origami."

40:16.500 --> 40:19.360
即使你收到消息了 我都不确定你是不是会回复
Even if you got the message, I wasn't sure you'd respond.

40:19.370 --> 40:21.090
我不能及时赶到你这儿了
I-I couldn't get to you in time.

40:21.100 --> 40:23.330
这是我唯一想得到的
This is the only thing I could think of.

40:23.340 --> 40:29.060
我发誓我会离开你 但我不得不联系你
I swore I'd leave you alone, but I had to contact you.

40:29.070 --> 40:31.790
因为我有什么东西么?
Because I have something?

40:31.800 --> 40:33.860
你怎么知道?
How'd you know?

40:33.870 --> 40:38.160
迈克尔  在基拉的时候 我的确要回到你身边的
Michael, back in Gila I was coming back to you.

40:38.170 --> 40:42.560
但有人抓住了我
Somebody... grabbed me, and they, um,

40:42.570 --> 40:45.460
我们告诉我父亲给了我些东西
they told me that my father had given me something.

40:45.470 --> 40:47.430
他们伤着你了?
Did someone hurt you?

40:47.440 --> 40:50.900
我逃走了
I-I got away.

40:53.600 --> 40:57.700
迈克尔  我希望这一切都能结束
Michael, I want for this to be over.

40:58.400 --> 41:00.360
我们两个都这样希望
That makes two of us.

41:00.370 --> 41:05.130
你认为这可能吗?
Do you think that's possible?

41:05.140 --> 41:06.790
如果有你的帮助  一定可以
With your help, yes.

41:06.800 --> 41:08.030
问题就在于你能不能看到
It's just a question of looking

41:08.040 --> 41:09.790
你父亲留给你的财富
at whatever it is your father gave you.

41:09.800 --> 41:13.200
这只是...
It's just...

41:13.640 --> 41:15.090
这只是一把钥匙啊
It's just a key.

41:15.100 --> 41:18.160
我们会弄清楚的
Well, we'll figure it out.

41:18.170 --> 41:19.370
我们一起
Together.

41:23.940 --> 41:27.870
我喜欢你这么说
I like the sound of that.

41:29.100 --> 41:30.570
我也是
Me, too.

41:47.300 --> 41:51.060
你好  保罗
Hello, Paul.

41:51.070 --> 41:53.730
总统女士  有段时间没看到你了
Madam President, it's been a while.

41:53.740 --> 41:54.990
我知道
I know.

41:55.000 --> 41:58.630
我打电话来道歉的
I'm calling to apologize.

41:58.640 --> 41:59.800
好吧
Okay.

42:00.300 --> 42:02.100
我非常抱歉
I'm so sorry

42:02.400 --> 42:05.430
一切都离我而去 可我最终却伤害了那个
It all just got away from me, and I ended up hurting

42:05.440 --> 42:08.190
一直陪伴我左右的人
the one person who's always been at my side.

42:08.200 --> 42:10.360
我希望你能回来  保罗
I want you to come home, Paul.

42:10.370 --> 42:11.790
我们能够解决这个问题的
We can fix this.

42:11.800 --> 42:13.130
我们一起
Together.

42:13.140 --> 42:15.930
而不是和那两个满世界逃亡
But not with those brothers running around the country

42:15.940 --> 42:21.100
搞垮在你帮助下建立起的公司的人
tearing down the very office you helped me build.

42:21.740 --> 42:23.130
卡罗琳...
Caroline...

42:23.140 --> 42:25.860
抓他们回来吧 保罗
Bring them in, Paul, and everything can go back

42:25.870 --> 42:28.000
这样一切都可以回到原来的状态
to the way it was.

42:33.440 --> 42:35.190
我得走了
I have to go now.

42:35.200 --> 42:38.840
我们尽快再联系
I'll see you soon.

42:44.940 --> 42:47.290
你和莎拉谈过了吗?
Did you talk to Sara?

42:47.300 --> 42:50.690
几天之内  不管是好是坏
In a few days, this should all be over,

42:50.700 --> 42:53.360
这一切都会结束了
one way or the other.

42:53.370 --> 42:54.840
当然
Absolutely.
